OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782908305
OL,3,CCornish charity poised to help people
OL,4,Cimpacted by Venezualan earthquakes
OL,6,FCornish charity ShelterBox is
OL,7,Fpreparing to help people affected by
OL,8,Fthe earthquakes in Venezuala.
OL,10,FTwo quakes of 7.2-7.5 magnitude hit
OL,11,Fthe South American country on
OL,12,FWednesday 24 June within minutes of
OL,13,Feach other, killing more than 1,400
OL,14,Fpeople.
OL,16,FThey were the strongest to hit the
OL,17,Fcountry in more than a century and
OL,18,Fcaused widespread destruction in the
OL,19,Fcapital, Caracas, and as far as
OL,20,FBrazil's Amazon, more than 1,000 miles
OL,21,Faway.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
