FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782908305
OL,3,CCornish charity poised to help people
OL,4,Cimpacted by Venezualan earthquakes
OL,6,FTens of thousands of people are
OL,7,Fwithout shelter and 68,000 have been
OL,8,Freported missing.
OL,10,FShelterBox, which is based in Truro,
OL,11,Fspecialises in distributing blankets,
OL,12,Fsleeping mats and shelter kits to
OL,13,Fpeople affected by natural disasters.
OL,15,FIt's responded to events in the region
OL,16,Fbefore, including in Haiti, Ecuador
OL,17,Fand Peru.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782908305
OL,3,CCornish charity poised to help people
OL,4,Cimpacted by Venezualan earthquakes
OL,6,FDave Raybould, the charity's emergency
OL,7,Fcoordinator, said: "We're a very small
OL,8,FCornish charity but we've got such a
OL,9,Fstrong reputation on the global
OL,10,Fplatform.
OL,12,F"So many people are aware of our work
OL,13,Fthat we do and look to us for support
OL,14,Fand guidance. It's humbling and I'm
OL,15,Fvery proud of the work we do. It is
OL,16,Fchallenging, but it's worth it."
OL,18,FWhat is the scale of the damage?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782908305
OL,3,CCornish charity poised to help people
OL,4,Cimpacted by Venezualan earthquakes
OL,6,FThe first earthquake struck near San
OL,7,FFelipe and, just 39 seconds later,
OL,8,Fanother hit near the town of Yumare,
OL,9,Fbetween 5 and 10km from the first.
OL,11,FIt's a scenario referred to as a
OL,12,F"doublet" by the US Geological Society.
OL,14,FStaff at ShelterBox say there has been
OL,15,Fextensive damage to buildings, homes,
OL,16,Ftransport networks and airports. Power
OL,17,Foutages and unreliable internet
OL,18,Fconnectivity have also made rescue
OL,19,Fefforts challenging, the charity said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782908305
OL,3,CCornish charity poised to help people
OL,4,Cimpacted by Venezualan earthquakes
OL,6,FAlthough the true impact on
OL,7,Fresidential areas isn't yet clear,
OL,8,Fthey say tens of thousands of people
OL,9,Fare likely to require emergency
OL,10,Fshelter and essential items.
OL,12,FDave Raybould added: "Having responded
OL,13,Fto similar events in highly populated
OL,14,Furban areas previously, such as in
OL,15,FTurkiye in 2023, we know how quickly
OL,16,Fthe scale of need can rise.
OL,18,F"Our job now is to work with our local
OL,19,Fpartners to make sure that the right
OL,20,Faid gets to the people most in need,
OL,21,Fas soon as possible.
OL,26,@wD@BxzzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
