PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782908305
OL,3,CCornish charity poised to help people
OL,4,Cimpacted by Venezualan earthquakes
OL,6,F"We store aid in Panama and other
OL,7,Fstrategic locations around the world,
OL,8,Fto make sure we're ready to respond
OL,9,Fwhen disasters like this happen."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
